UID:51ee364679d4cf98f0b32488d035faab@events.in.gov
DESCRIPTION:Did you know that not all fur is the same? Different animals u
 se their fur for camoflauge\, protection\, and keeping warm in a variety o
 f habitats. Visit the Nature Center to learn about Indiana&#39\;s native m
 ammals. Learn about their habits\, habitats\, play a short game\, and touc
 h real animal furs!
